video.title: Fast & Furious Spy Racers
video.synopsis: A government agency recruits teen driver Tony Toretto and his thrill-seeking friends to infiltrate a criminal street racing circuit as undercover spies.

episodes.synopsis: Tony is pumped when his legendary cousin Dom recruits him and his friends for an exciting mission: to infiltrate a secret street racing circuit.
episodes.title: Born a Toretto

episodes.synopsis: After Tony rocks it against Layla in a thrilling race through LA, SH1FT3R boss Shashi invites Tony's crew to join his group by pulling a job for him.
episodes.title: Enter SH1FT3R

episodes.synopsis: Tony takes on all the SH1FT3R racers in a remote ghost town. But Tony's real mission isnâ€™t to win -- it's to track what scheme Shashi's up to.
episodes.title: Ghost Town Grand Prix

episodes.synopsis: While Tony works with Layla and Shashi to steal codes from a Russian businessman, Ms. Nowhere sends the others to snoop around Shashi's mansion.
episodes.title: The Owl Job

episodes.synopsis: The crew enters a SH1FT3R race up a privately owned mountain. Can they find out what Shashi wants at the summit without blowing their cover?
episodes.title: The Celestial Vault

episodes.synopsis: Ms. Nowhere tells the crew that the mission is over, but Tony isn't ready to give up. He's too much of a Toretto to back off now.
episodes.title: The Final Key

episodes.synopsis: When the crew takes over an amazing spy plane, they meet Shashi in the desert to exchange precious cargo. Will they also learn Shashi's master plan?
episodes.title: Ignition

episodes.synopsis: It's up to Tony and his crew to save the world when Shashi sets up a showdown with evil billionaire Cleve Kelso on the Las Vegas strip.
episodes.title: The Key to the Strip

episodes.synopsis: When the Spy Racers make a big bust in LA, they learn about a secret operation in Brazil and plead with Ms. Nowhere to let them go undercover.
episodes.title: Escape from L.A.

episodes.synopsis: After arriving in Brazil, the crew gets their ride stuck in quicksand. But Tony's determined to get them out of trouble without Ms. Nowhereâ€™s help.
episodes.title: That Sinking Feeling

episodes.synopsis: The Spy Racers explore Rio hoping to find the gang that captured Layla, but soon have to question if sheâ€™s on their side or has turned against them.

episodes.synopsis: After Frostee discovers that the secret formula is explosive, Tony and Echo go into overdrive to find a tanker full of it before it blows up Rio.
episodes.title: Combustion

episodes.synopsis: An old friend helps the team figure out whoâ€™s behind the evil plan, then makes a shocking discovery after a hair-raising race in the streets.

episodes.synopsis: On a dangerous mission to recover the hauler, Echo has to think quick on her feet to avoid capture by a surprising enemy.

episodes.synopsis: As a plan comes together to unleash the formula on an unsuspecting public, the Spy Racers scramble to stop it.

episodes.synopsis: With an angry mob on their tail, the team must pull out all the stops to recover the spy plane and save the world from a chilling reign of terror.
episodes.title: Tchau, Uggos

episodes.synopsis: Tony can't figure out why Echo was picked over him for spy school. Ms. Nowhere and Gary pursue a trio of familiar villains in Africa.
episodes.title: The Giant Haboob

episodes.synopsis: Echo leads the Spy Racers to the Sahara to find Cleve Kelso, but when they're all captured, Layla and Tony must win a dune buggy race for their freedom.

episodes.synopsis: The Spy Racers help a village with a water well that's run dry. Meanwhile, Ms. Nowhere and Gary try to make contact from the middle of... nowhere.

episodes.synopsis: With Kelso's lair in their sights, the team gets dragged into an epic dune buggy chase through the desert. Layla clashes with an old enemy.
episodes.title: The Hunt

episodes.synopsis: A hurricane in the Sahara? The team finds shelter with a group of Bedouins to escape a storm's wrath. Ms. Nowhere and Gary make an unexpected discovery.

episodes.synopsis: As Kelso closes in on his evil goals, the Spy Racers face a tough decision in the remote desert. Will they follow their heads or their hearts?
episodes.title: The Eye of the Sahara

episodes.synopsis: Minus one key member, the team makes a final push to infiltrate Kelso's base to stop him from unleashing his diabolical plan.
episodes.title: RoboCleve

episodes.synopsis: The showdown in the Sahara comes to a fiery end when a swirling megastorm threatens to take out everything in its path â€” including the Spy Racers.
episodes.title: Sirocco Fire Explosion

episodes.synopsis: Ms. Nowhere is rewarded with a party at headquarters when a worldwide chase leads to a big capture. But the celebration may be short-lived.
episodes.title: Chasing Phantoms

episodes.synopsis: Frostee works to bring Ms. Nowhere and the Spy Racers to safety. And now that the agency had turned on all of them, it's time to go rogue.
episodes.title: The Convoy

episodes.synopsis: On the run and facing a shortage of money, the crew turns to what they do best â€” racing! â€” to earn enough cash to get them to Mexico City.

episodes.synopsis: The Spy Racers are once again racing against the clock, this time to stop Mexico City from being destroyed by Moray's fiery volcano machine!

episodes.synopsis: Deep in lava-filled tunnels under the city, the Spy Racers make one last stand against Moray to stop his evil plan once and for all.
episodes.title: Don't Go Chasing Lavafalls

episodes.synopsis: The Spy Racers get caught up in playing a new virtual reality video game. But fun turns into frustration when Tony doesn't act like a good teammate.
episodes.title: R.O.A.M. Around the World

episodes.synopsis: With one of their own in danger at the hands of their old enemy Sudarikov, the Spy Racers take to the sky for a daring aerial rescue.
episodes.title: The Rescue

episodes.synopsis: From high in the sky to deep in the water! With a barrage of torpedoes on their tail, can the Spy Racers engineer an undersea escape?

episodes.synopsis: Stranded on an island in the South Pacific, the team plots its next move while trying to help Tony overcome his mysterious inability to drive.
episodes.title: Driving and Crying

episodes.synopsis: Ms. Nowhere believes Shashi holds the information the team needs, so she agrees to free him for a day â€” even though the others doubt he can be trusted.

episodes.synopsis: Layla, Tony and Shashi attempt to infiltrate Sudarikovâ€™s island base. Elsewhere, the others struggle to rein in their out-of-control spy plane.

episodes.title: The Takeover

episodes.synopsis: To stop the virus from taking over the world, the Spy Racers will have to come together as a family to battle the most familiar foe theyâ€™ve ever faced.
episodes.title: The Toretto Virus
